BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:18SnMtmYlxJhHh0Pb7ZMx
SUMMARY:Blue Monday #3: Del Rey & The Kings of Mongrel Folk
DTSTAMP:20260321T222801Z
DTSTART:20260331T023000Z
DESCRIPTION:Del Rey\, known for her amazing instrumental skills on guitar a
	nd ukulele always provides a very entertaining show\, full of variety\, dr
	ama and humor.   Great songs\, virtuoso harmonica\, soulful blues\, hot pi
	ckin' and sweet country vocals - that's what you get when Orville Johnson 
	and Mark Graham combine forces as the Kings of Mongrel Folk. Doors at 6:30
	\, Show at 7:30\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/blue-mond
	ay-3-del-rey-the-kings-of-mongrel-folk/18252366/2026-03-30T00\n\nFrom SEAt
	oday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/blue-monday-3-del-rey-the
