	nd ukulele always provides a very entertaining show\, full of variety\, dr
	ama and humor.   Great songs\, virtuoso harmonica\, soulful blues\, hot pi
	ckin' and sweet country vocals - that's what you get when Orville Johnson 
	and Mark Graham combine forces as the Kings of Mongrel Folk. Doors at 6:30
